  "architecture_summary": "Qwen2.5-VL is a vision-language model series built around a native dynamic-resolution Vision Transformer with Window Attention, 2D-RoPE, and an MLP-based vision-language merger, initialized from the pre-trained Qwen2.5 LLM. It adds dynamic FPS sampling and absolute-time-aligned MRoPE for video understanding, and is trained with large-scale pre-training plus SFT and DPO post-training.",
